316
00:25:48.890 --> 00:25:50.224
Well. I'm okay with that if you are.

317
00:25:50.307 --> 00:25:51.598
I said that's what I wanna do.

318
00:25:51.682 --> 00:25:53.598
- not what I'm gonna do.
- Oh. come on. we can...

319
00:25:53.682 --> 00:25:56.390
