over the hole to cover it.

320
00:25:56.473 --> 00:25:58.431
bring in a piece of Sheetrock tomorrow.

321
00:25:58.515 --> 00:26:00.974
I'm handy. I can help you patch it up.
nobody'll know the difference.

322
00:26:01.057 --> 00:26:04.140
- Why would we do that?
- I have a very curious nature.

323
00:26:04.224 --> 00:26:06.015
Clearly. No. I don't think so.

324
00:26:10.224 --> 00:26:11.266
It's my...

325
00:26:12.307 --> 00:26:13.557
kid's dad.

326
00:26:15.182 --> 00:26:17.598
High school. Shit happens.

327
00:26:18.224 --> 00:26:19.723
Yeah. That it does.

328
00:26:21.473 --> 00:26:23.807
He is a hopeless man-child.

329
00:26:23.890 --> 00:26:27.598
and that sort of shit
makes me wanna smash through walls.

330
00:26:27.682 --> 00:26:30.348
- Let's. let's do it.
- So we can see a dead smoke alarm?

331
00:26:30.431 --> 00:26:33.723
