366
00:28:39.932 --> 00:28:42.682
I don't have any equipment.
I need everything on the list.

367
00:28:42.765 --> 00:28:44.598
I'm sorry. Mr. Quinn.

368
00:28:44.682 --> 00:28:48.557
- I'm just not familiar with...
- I wrote an ECI white paper in 2009.

369
00:28:48.640 --> 00:28:51.848
It's compartmented
and stored in a clean vault.

370
00:28:52.431 --> 00:28:55.723
Read the report and have
everything listed in Appendix A

371
00:28:55.807 --> 00:28:59.598
