Understood?

372
00:28:59.682 --> 00:29:02.099
I can't do all that
without multiple authorizations.

373
00:29:02.181 --> 00:29:05.473
Listen to me.
This fungus is intensely adaptable.

374
00:29:05.557 --> 00:29:08.682
It will mutate and spread
in unpredictable ways.

375
00:29:08.765 --> 00:29:11.682
Get Gordon Gray to clear you.
Only Gordon Gray.

376
00:29:11.765 --> 00:29:13.223
Don't call anyone else.

377
00:29:15.390 --> 00:29:16.682
